      <h2>Best Lounge Access Credit Cards in India</h2>
      <p>Airport lounge access is one of the most valued credit card perks in India. A single lounge visit costs ₹1,500-₹2,500 if paid out of pocket, and frequent travellers can spend ₹15,000-₹30,000+ per year on lounges alone. Lounge access credit cards include complimentary visits as part of the card benefits, saving you significant money while upgrading your airport experience with hot meals, premium beverages, shower facilities, and quiet workspaces.</p>
      <p>Cards provide lounge access through programs like Priority Pass, Dreamfolks, Mastercard Lounge Program, or Visa Airport Companion. The number of free visits ranges from 2 per quarter (entry-level) to unlimited (super-premium cards like HDFC Infinia and Diners Club Black).</p>

      <h2>Key Features of Lounge Access Cards</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Priority Pass Membership:</strong> Access to 1,300+ lounges in 600+ cities across 150+ countries worldwide</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Domestic Lounge Access:</strong> Free visits at 50+ domestic airport lounges via Dreamfolks or bank-specific programs</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Guest Access:</strong> Some cards allow you to bring 1-2 guests for free per visit</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Premium Amenities:</strong> Hot buffet meals, premium beverages, Wi-Fi, shower rooms, and quiet relaxation areas</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Meet & Greet Services:</strong> Super-premium cards include airport assistance and fast-track immigration at select airports</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Railway Lounge Access:</strong> Some cards also provide access to railway station lounges across India</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Top 5 Lounge Access Credit Cards for 2026</h2>
      <table class="rate-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Card Name</th><th>Annual Fee</th><th>Lounge Visits</th><th>Key Benefits</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
