      <h2>Eligibility for Lounge Access Cards</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Age:</strong> 21-60 years (salaried) or 21-65 years (self-employed); some premium cards require 25+</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Income:</strong> ₹30,000/month for basic lounge cards (4 visits); ₹1,00,000+/month for unlimited access cards</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Credit Score:</strong> 730+ CIBIL for most lounge access cards; 750+ for super-premium unlimited access cards</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Travel Frequency:</strong> Banks may consider your travel history when issuing premium lounge access cards</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Existing Relationship:</strong> Having a savings/FD account with the bank significantly improves approval chances</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Documents:</strong> PAN, Aadhaar, passport, income proof, and recent bank statements</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>How to Apply for a Lounge Access Card</h3>
